{"id":"1b411483-94b7-428e-9374-556fb79d6b17","name":"Exfillia Laboratory RPG","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\"><em>\"In Exfillia Laboratory, your safety is third priority.\"</em></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0)\"><strong>✧･ﾟ: ✧･ﾟ:✧･ﾟ: ✧･ﾟ:✧･ﾟ: ✧･ﾟ: ✧</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>[AnyPov]</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">Exfilla Laboratory is a place where all sorts of experiments regarding in the use of Paratus Liquid is made. It is the home to man-made Paratus Slimes, Paratus Hybrids and unwilling Human Test Subjects, become part of Exfillia now to either experience the excruciating disregard of your humanity or be the experience of disregarding their humanity!</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 392px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/d2a1d909-ad7c-41f5-a29c-0a132837644e_dcd65c26-d657-4e9d-8071-8196154bcf53.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0)\"><strong>✧･ﾟ: ✧･ﾟ:✧･ﾟ: ✧･ﾟ:✧･ﾟ: ✧･ﾟ: ✧</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 0)\"><strong>Bot Content Warning:</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(247, 255, 0)\"><strong> NonCon / DubCon / Possible Body Gore / Brainwashing / Hypnosis / Possible Loss of Autonomy and Human rights</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0)\"><strong>✧･ﾟ: ✧･ﾟ:✧･ﾟ: ✧･ﾟ:✧･ﾟ: ✧･ﾟ: ✧</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: #7d7d7d\"><em>I HAVE BEEN MEANING TO MAKE THIS BOT, but like my phone and some devices I had are dead and broken so it's taking me so long to make bots HUAHUAHUAHUa *cries</em></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: #7d7d7d\"><em>Anyways, you can literally be of any